OL,3,CLeicester City star fined #20k for
OL,4,Cdrink-driving in wife's Range Rover
OL,6,Fstar Hamza Choudhury has been fined
OL,7,F#20,000 after a court heard he was
OL,8,Fcaught drink-driving on the wrong side
OL,9,Fof the road in his wife's Range Rover.
OL,11,FNottingham Magistrates' Court was
OL,12,Fshown police dashcam footage of the 26-
OL,13,Fyear-old being pulled over in
OL,14,FLoughborough Road, West Bridgford,
OL,15,FNottingham, in the early hours of
OL,16,FFriday 19 January.
OL,18,FThe midfielder, of Edwalton,
OL,19,FNottinghamshire, pleaded guilty to
OL,20,Fdriving while double the legal alcohol
OL,21,Flimit and careless driving.
