OL,4,Cdrink-driving in wife's Range Rover
OL,6,FHe was also given a 40-month driving
OL,7,Fban, and ordered to pay a #2,000
OL,8,Fvictim surcharge and #85 in
OL,9,Fprosecution costs.
OL,11,FThe 40-month ban would be reduced by
OL,12,Faround nine months if he completes a
OL,13,Fdrink-driving rehabilitation course.
OL,15,FDefence lawyer Kally Sohata told the
OL,16,Fcourt Choudhury had shared a taxi home
OL,17,Ffrom a restaurant with a friend, but
OL,18,Fhad returned in his wife's car after
OL,19,Frealising he had left his phone behind.
