OL,6,FPassing sentence, District Judge Sunil
OL,7,FKhanna told Choudhury, who earns
OL,8,F#12,000 a week: "I do accept that this
OL,9,Fwill impact you and that you are
OL,10,Fextremely embarrassed by what has
OL,11,Foccurred."
OL,13,FThe 26-year-old started Leicester
OL,14,FCity's 1-0 win against Bournemouth on
OL,15,FTuesday 27 February, in the fifth
OL,16,Fround of the FA Cup.
OL,18,FHis side are currently top of the
OL,19,FChampionship after relegation from the
OL,20,Flast season.
