OL,6,FProsecutor Ben Payne told the court
OL,7,FChoudhury had a previous drink-driving
OL,8,Fconviction dating back to 2017,
OL,9,Fmeaning the player faced a mandatory
OL,10,Fban of at least three years.
OL,12,FMr Payne told the court that a charge
OL,13,Fof failing to co-operate with a
OL,14,Froadside breath test had been
OL,15,Fwithdrawn.
